```

inside

```
data/raw/
```

5. Run notebooks in order:

```
01_EDA.ipynb

↓

02_data_preprocessing.ipynb

↓

03_model_training.ipynb

↓

04_model_comparison.ipynb

↓

05_final_analysis.ipynb
```

